steps.title: Create Your Character
steps.description: Start by configuring your character's visual and audio identity in this modal.

steps.title: Add Reference Images
steps.description: Upload up to two images to define your character's visual appearance. Our AI will combine features for consistency.

steps.title: Give Your Character a Name
steps.description: Enter a unique and memorable name for your character, like 'Cyber-Ronin'.

steps.title: Define Personality and Role
steps.description: Describe your Character's Appearance & Personality.  (Pro Tip: clicking edit on an existing Character to see how their description is clearly structure in 2 parts.  Who they are both mentally and physically in 2 very distinct paragraphs.)

steps.title: Choose an AI Voice
steps.description: Select an AI voice from the drop down that best suits your character's persona and traits.

steps.title: Save Your New Character
steps.description: Once you're happy with all the details, click 'Save to Vault' to add your character to your collection.
